    {
        "content": "<p>(And on that note, how come <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Minimal.IsLeast#doc\">docs#Minimal.IsLeast</a> for linear orders doesn't exist?)</p>",
